<collectingCountry id="0AF6767C2451BD08FAB3DD341E4FA091" box="[1299,1392,886,912]" name="Panama" pageId="79" pageNumber="80">Panama</collectingCountry>
at 1243(1100–1450) m elevation in montane rainforest (
